obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line 4
  line `THE ADVOCATES ACT, 1961`
  line `ACT NO. 25 OF 1961`
  line `[19 th May, 1961.]`
  line `An Act to amend and consolidate the law relating to the legal practitioners and to provide for the`
  line `constitution of Bar Councils and an All - India Bar.`
  line `B E it enacted by Parliament in the Twelfth Year of the Republic of India as follows:―`
  line `CHAPTER I`
  line `P RELIMINARY`
  line `1. Short title, extent and commencement. ― ( 1 ) This Act may be called the Advocates Act, 1961.`
  line `1 [ ( 2 ) It extends to the whole of India.]`
  line `( 3 ) It 2 [shall, in relation to the territories other than those referred to in sub - section ( 4 ), come into force]`
  line `on such date 3 as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, appoint, and diff erent`
  line `dates 3 may be appointed for different provisions of this Act.`
  line `4 [( 4 ) This Act shall, in relation to the State of Jammu and Kashmir * 5 and the Union territory of Goa,`
  line `Daman and Diu, come into force on such date as the Central Government may, by notific ation in the Official`
  line `Gazette, appoint in this behalf, and different dates may be appointed for different provisions of this Act.]`
  line `2. Definitions. ― 6 [( 1 )] In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires, ―`
  line `1. Subs. by Act 60 of 1973, s. 2, for sub - section ( 2 ) (w.e.f. 31 - 1 - 1974).`
  line `2. Subs. by s. 2, ibid., for “shall come into force” (w.e.f. 31 - 1 - 1974).`
  line `3. The provisions of the A ct have been brought into force as under:―`
  line `16th August, 1961, vide notification No. S. O. 1870, dated 7th September, 1961, in respect of Chapter I, II and VII, see Gazette of`
  line `India, Ex trao rdinary, Part II, sec. 3( ii ).`
  line `1st December, 1961, vide notification No. S.O. 2790, dated 24th November, 1961, in respect of Chapter III and s. 50( 2 ), see`
  line `Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3( ii ).`
  line `15th December, 1961, vide notification No. S.O. 2919, dated 13th December, 1961, in respect of s. 50( 1 ), see Gazet te of India,`
  line `Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3 ( ii ).`
  line `24th January, 1962, vide notification No. S.O. 297, dated 24th January 1962, in respect of s s. 5 1 and 52, see Gazette of India,`
  line `Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3 ( ii ).`
  line `29th March, 1962, vide notification No. S.O. 958, dated 29th March 1962, in respect of s. 46, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary,`
  line `Part II, sec. ( ii ).`
  line `4th January, 1963, vide notification No. S.O. 50, dated 4th January 1963, in respect of s. 32 and Chapter V I [ except s. 46,`
  line `su b - section s ( 1 ) and ( 2 ) of s. 50, ss. 51 and 52 ], see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3 ( ii ).`
  line `1st September, 1963, vide notification No. S.O. 2509, dated 31st August, 1963, in respect of Chapter V, see Gazette of India,`
  line `Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3 ( ii ).`
  line `10th June, 1968, vide notification No. S.O. 63, dated 7th June 1968, in respect of Chapter s I, II, III, section 32 of Chapter IV and`
  line `Chapters V, VI, VII and VIII in the Union territory of Pondicherry, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3 ( ii ).`
  line `1st June, 1969, vide notification No. S.O. 1500, dated 5th April, 1969, in respect of s s. 29, 31, 33 and 34 of Chapter IV, see`
  line `Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3 ( ii ).`
  line `1 st June, 1979, vide notification No. G.S.R. 84 (E), dated 2 1st February 1979, e xcept section 30 in respect of the Union territory`
  line `of Goa, Daman and Diu, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3 ( i ).`
  line `15th June, 2011, vide notification No. S.O. 1349(E), dated 9th June, 2011, in respect of section 30, see Gazette of India,`
  line `Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3( i ).`
  line `4. Ins. by Act 60 of 1973, s. 2 (w.e.f. 31 - 1 - 1974).`
  line `5. 1 st August 1986, vide notification No. G.S.R. 946 (E), dated 15th July 1986, except section 30, in respect of the State of Jammu and`
  line `Kash mir.`
  line `6. Se ction 2 re numbered as sub - section ( 1 ) of that section by Act 60 of 1973, s. 3 (w.e.f. 31 - 1 - 1974).`
  line `*. Vide notification No. S.O. 3912(E), dated 30th October, 2019, this Act is made applicable to the Union territory of Jammu and`
  line `Kashmir and the Union territo ry of Ladakh.`
obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_5:
  kind page
  sectionId pdf-page-5
