obj_root_law_sections_36_content:
  string
  line 36
  line `THE SCHEDULE`
  line `[ See section 50( 5 )]`
  line `R EPEAL OF CERTAIN ENACTMENTS`
  line `Short title Extent of repeal`
  line `1. The Legal Practitioners (Women) Act, 1923 (23 of 1923) The whole.`
  line `2. The Legal Practitioners (Fees) Act, 1926 (21 of 1926) The whole.`
  line `3. The States Reorganisation Act, 1956 (37 of 1956) Section 53.`
  line `4. The Bombay Reorganisation Act, 1960 (11 of 1960) Section 31.`
